[section#depr.capture.this
    [:en] Implicit capture of [`*this] by reference
    [:zh_CN] 按引用隐式捕获 [`*this]
]

[para]
[:en] For compatibility with prior [=Cpp] International Standards, a lambda
expression with [~capture-default] [`=] ([#expr.prim.lambda.capture]) may
implicitly capture [`*this] by reference.
[:zh_CN] 为维持与更早的 [=Cpp] 国际标准的兼容性，带有[~默认捕获符] [`=]
（[#expr.prim.lambda.capture]）的 lambda 表达式可能按引用隐式捕获 [`*this]。

[enter:example]
[codeblock]
struct X {
  int x;
  void foo(int n) {
    auto f = [=]() { x = n; };          // [:en] deprecated: [`x] means [`this->x], not a copy thereof
                                        // [|:zh_CN] 被摒弃：[`x] 的意思是 [`this->x]，而不是其副本
    auto g = [=, this]() { x = n; };    // [:en] recommended replacement
                                        // [|:zh_CN] 推荐的替代方案
  }
};
[codeblock:end]
[exit:example]
